snippet.title: CellFactor: Psychokinetic Wars Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description: CellFactor: Psychokinetic Wars combines single-player and multiplayer components into one action-packed downloadable title for Xbox LIVE Arcade for Xbox 360 and PlayStation Network. Complete with next-gen graphics and robust gameplay, CellFactor: Psychokinetic Wars allows players to wage war by using their choice of gunfire and/or telekinetic superpowers. Players can use telekinetic energy to rip objects from the surrounding environment and hurl them at enemies or draw on their powers to create a bullet-proof energy shield that protects against gunfire. Flying, teleporting and accelerated speed abilities give players countless ways to fight the good fight with four multiplayer modes (DeathMatch, Capture the Flag, Team Death Match and Assault) and a deep single-player campaign with 30 solo challenges.
